{"tid":2251613,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"喺屋企都可以參加富士山馬拉松","createTime":"2020-10-21T02:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T15:31:05.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"22ec3e02b42eac284632819a13ec6816113240fc","tid":2251613,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:26:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmtfujimarathon.com%2Fenglish%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=a4b7dfdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/events/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmtfujimarathon.com%2Fenglish%2Fevents%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=8698a845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/events/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/running_marathon_mountfujimarathon_20200731_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2Frunning_marathon_mountfujimarathon_20200731_04.jpg&h=5c619396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n富士山馬拉松係圍住富士山山腳跑<br />\n但因為習總令武肺襲地球，所以好多馬拉松都取消<br />\n呢個都唔例外<br />\n但係今年會方推出網上虛擬跑開放比全球選手參加<br />\n好似平時馬拉松咁有全馬，半馬，10k，5k<br />\n<br />\n而最特別係個馬拉松為期<strong><span class=\"red\">10日</span></strong>  (21/11 ~ 30/11)<br />\n點解係為期10日呢？<br />\n因為佢唔需要你一次跑完<br />\n10日內你跑完你報既長度就得<br />\ne.g. 我報10k，我一日跑1k都可以，當然你一日跑完都可以啦<br />\n<br />\n只要點樣知道你跑完全程"},{"pid":"4103b154a83a2870d63f4214923ba4b88548e5d4","tid":2251613,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:32:22.000Z","msg":"未打完就出左post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點樣知道你跑完全程<br />\n只要你跑既時候用自己跑步app紀錄<br />\n跑完之後cap低個record send比佢就ok！<br />\n<br />\n報名費算係普通啦<br />\n全馬 6,500羊<br />\n半馬以下 5,500羊<br />\n<br />\n至於<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">獎品方面</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/wp-content/uploads/img/tatta/tshrit_img.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmtfujimarathon.com%2Fenglish%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimg%2Ftatta%2Ftshrit_img.jpg&h=ff9b8878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/wp-content/uploads/img/tatta/medal01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmtfujimarathon.com%2Fenglish%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimg%2Ftatta%2Fmedal01.jpg&h=9549f3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/wp-content/uploads/img/tatta/medal02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmtfujimarathon.com%2Fenglish%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimg%2Ftatta%2Fmedal02.jpg&h=1bc6f414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/wp-content/uploads/img/tatta/medal03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmtfujimarathon.com%2Fenglish%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimg%2Ftatta%2Fmedal03.jpg&h=d76cf48a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/wp-content/uploads/img/tatta/result_card_sample.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmtfujimarathon.com%2Fenglish%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimg%2Ftatta%2Fresult_card_sample.jpg&h=d2617f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑完之後會有張cert，有件紀念tee同埋有個牌仔送比你！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/34XGr3TH5hM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F34XGr3TH5hM&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=a159451e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/34XGr3TH5hM</a><br />\n如果你係跑全馬，仲會send多條片比你模擬你喺當地跑！<br />\n<br />\n如果想報名，入上面條link就可以<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">11月10就截止啦！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"66b1a216fbef5bacf51b8595f978eaffa013370b","tid":2251613,"uid":14983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:35:25.000Z","msg":"抗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594d22b4036c2ac0106cac0334b00ba9a1b29ba4","tid":2251613,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"即係三百幾蚊送件衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢寄過嚟啊？"},{"pid":"f532ed7a5b356cae6d8b2c33dc1934711d2aff7b","tid":2251613,"uid":32716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"當年跑過 條賽道真係好靚好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3624640c1fba009b6171c2f060fa87d5241a156a","tid":2251613,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594d22b4036c2ac0106cac0334b00ba9a1b29ba4","tid":2251613,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"即係三百幾蚊送件衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢寄過嚟啊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:31:00.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n仲有個獎牌"},{"pid":"6b9518a12656003ac8ece6411f981bf31eedfb21","tid":2251613,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4103b154a83a2870d63f4214923ba4b88548e5d4","tid":2251613,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:32:22.000Z","msg":"未打完就出左post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點樣知道你跑完全程<br />\n只要你跑既時候用自己跑步app紀錄<br />\n跑完之後cap低個record send比佢就ok！<br />\n<br />\n報名費算係普通啦<br />\n全馬 6,500羊<br />\n半馬以下 5,500羊<br />\n<br />\n至於<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">獎品方面</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/wp-content/uploads/img/tatta/tshrit_img.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmtfujimarathon.com%2Fenglish%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fimg%2Ftatta%2Ftshrit_img.jpg&h=ff9b8878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://mtfujimarathon.com/english/wp